{"tid":1868422,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"個乜柒武漢醫生死鳩咗唯有講句唔好彩，仲話傷心嘅人根本就係on 9","createTime":"2020-02-07T14:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T00:07:44.000Z","uid":81190,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fcb575739573058a9a7c6eda7ad2b5f0aa1527a","tid":1868422,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"我真係唔係好明俾咩傷心，要求平咩反<br />\n<br />\n一開頭個個喊打喊殺，之後真係愈嚟愈多人都確診先話捉錯人。到今日條撚屌死鳩咗中紀委先話查人。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母姐係中央一早知捉錯人啦。<br />\n<br />\n「深切哀悼」同文革鬥錯人鬥死人先道歉一模一撚樣。<br />\n再難聽啲講句，呢場肺炎大陸死咗一億人都仲有十幾億人，強制生育呢一億人即刻就有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哀悼？我去哀悼義士仲好。<br />\n強國為咗搞共和死咗咁撚多人都搞到咁，班大陸喱就真係要哀悼啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SC5VUbv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSC5VUbv.png&h=281885af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed211dc7b055dae94b7d05b1dceb23e289653118","tid":1868422,"uid":127571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"796048f3d0dd22bb58f1979a6cf09193b01fd270","tid":1868422,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:40:48.000Z","msg":"你好似混淆左官同民"},{"pid":"0d3940a75e3643f68c1971a9c670a5da8e20ef23","tid":1868422,"uid":268774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T19:41:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aadec96497f44ab37197188cdda789cb8611357f","tid":1868422,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T00:07:44.000Z","msg":"消費下個醫生嘛"}]}